This is my VIM configure available for MacVim/Gvim 7.3+ and it could run cross different platforms including Windows and *nix. If you love my configure or have some questions about this configure, please feel free to contact me! Thank you!

If you want to install this configure in your computer, please run these commands in your terminal:
1 git clone http://github.com/gmarik/vundle.git $HOME/.vim/bundle/vundle
2 git clone http://github.com/kepbod/kepbod-vim-configure.git $HOME/vimrc
3 cp $HOME/vimrc/.vimrc $HOME/.vimrc
4 vim .vimrc
5 :BundleInstall!
6 Just enjoy it!

PS: This configure needs git support exuberant ctags installed and Ack.vim require Perl module App::Ack, and you can check :help Ack.txt for more details.
